Information

Each file is symbolized by a circle. Size of the circle represents the Cyclomatic complexity. Color of the circle represents the Maintainability Index.

Large red circles will be probably hard to maintain.

This score is not absolute. This chart is a comparison of your project relative to a representative average of recent PHP projects.

Each score is calculated from various criterias from 1322 files in your projects. Your score is a note between 0 (poor) and 100 (excellent).
